Key Match Events: Guerschon Yabusele sealed the win with a block on Bilal Coulibaly in the final seconds of the game
Post-Match Reflections: Guerschon Yabusele praised his late-game block, saying he had a good feeling and bumped Coulibaly to lose his balance
Miscellaneous Highlights: Joel Embiid and Andre Drummond were out of action against the Wizards
Yabusele put together a strong outing with 21 points, eight rebounds, and three assists
Others: The Sixers will be back in action on Friday night to take on Zion Williamson and the New Orleans Pelicans
